org.opends.sdk.responses
Interface Response

All Known Subinterfaces:
BindResult, CompareResult, ExtendedResult, GenericExtendedResult, GenericIntermediateResponse, IntermediateResponse, Result, SearchResultEntry, SearchResultReference
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractExtendedResult, AbstractIntermediateResponse, GetConnectionIDResult, PasswordModifyResult, PasswordPolicyStateExtendedOperation.Response, WhoAmIResult
public interface Response

The base class of all Responses provides methods for querying and manipulating the set of Controls included with a Response.
